 Act i.e. \"Obamacare\". Both laws were pushed and advocated under false pretenses. Therefore they were fraudulent at their core, and advanced as legislation for the sole purpose that the government could garner clandestine revenue. \nThis new revelation can be used as a wedge of legal precedent for the destruction of the ACA I can only pray some one sees it...", "author": "Alpha-Kil0", "created": 1775917485086, "profile_picture": "nFm7nABf3gi8", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "UltimatePistachio", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "", "removal_source": "", "link": "", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "Why the Moonshine ruling might be bigger than you realize. ", "last_comment_created": 1775954367935, "content": "<p>The 158 year ban on home distilling has been overturned due to its unconstitutional existence as an ad-hoc tax.\nDuring Prohibition federal officers hunted down moonshiners not because the liquor they were making was dangerous, unsanitary, or even immoral, but it was a way working class people could make a cash income that the government couldn't take a cut of. That was something the government just couldn't allow.</p>\n<p>Fast forward to the modern day what &quot;law&quot; exists as a tax and that is the very nature by which it was allowed to become law? The Affordable Care Act i.e. &quot;Obamacare&quot;. Both laws were pushed and advocated under false pretenses. Therefore they were fraudulent at their core, and advanced as legislation for the sole purpose that the government could garner clandestine revenue.\nThis new revelation can be used as a wedge of legal precedent for the destruction of the ACA I can only pray some one sees it...</p>\n", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 24, "score_up": 181, "is_edited": true, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"status": 200}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "2043010021735182687", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "link", "uuid": "1ASZMK5Xhl", "is_twitter": true, "is_admin": false, "score": 89, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8551825, "raw_content": "", "author": "_Liberty_Prime_", "created": 1775931370958, "profile_picture": "evWxa80vv4JN", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "Mungo", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "twitter.com", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "https://media.scored.co/preview/1ASZMK5Xhl.png", "removal_source": "", "link": "https://twitter.com/WhiteHouse/status/2043010021735182687?s=20", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "Greatest Country in the History of the Planet.", "last_comment_created": 1775936477382, "content": "", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 2, "score_up": 89, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"twitter": {"quotedTweet": false, "images": [{"width": 960, "heightRatio": 125, "url": "https://pbs.twimg.com/media/HFo6xkvWwAAJyqV.jpg", "height": 1200}, {"width": 960, "heightRatio": 125, "url": "https://pbs.twimg.com/media/HFo6xkwWUAAqmZ_.jpg", "height": 1200}, {"width": 960, "heightRatio": 125, "url": "https://pbs.twimg.com/media/HFo6xkvW0AEp1KN.jpg", "height": 1200}, {"width": 960, "heightRatio": 125, "url": "https://pbs.twimg.com/media/HFo6xkzWUAAmfyi.jpg", "height": 1200}], "linkEmbed": false, "replies": 505, "created": 1775926521000, "id": "2043010021735182687", "video": false, "poll": 